releaseNotes:
1.3.4 2025-02-22 kkossev  - added TS0601 _TZE284_nlrfgpny in TuyaSolarAlarm group;
1.3.3 2024-11-20 - added TS0601 _TZE204_hcxvyxa5 and _TZE204_q76rtoa9 in Tuya group;
1.3.2 2024-10-09 - debug enabled;  added Refresh() command; setMelody(); setDuration(); stop(); both(); siren(); strobe();
1.3.1 2024-10-08 - restored the overwritten code changes in the previous version;
1.3.0 2024-10-07 - setVolume bug fix; adding Tuya Solar Alarm '_TZE200_nlrfgpny', '_TZE204_nlrfgpny'
1.2.2 2023-07-19 - fix: moved _TZE204_t1blo2bj in Tuya group;
1.2.1 2023-05-26 - added _TZE204_t1blo2bj in Neo group; installed() bug fix;
1.2.0 2023-01-22 - _TZE200_d0yu2xgi (NEO) experimental support including temperature and humidity; added separate preferences for alarm and Melody, Volume and Duration
1.1.2 2022-12-31 - bug fix: the sounds titles changes in the previous version could make the siren freeze!; Import button changed to the development branch
1.1.1 2022-12-27 - bug fix: playing a sound from RM rule without specifying the volume level was making the device freeze; debug logs cleanup; sounds titles improvements;
1.1.0 2022-11-05 - Alarm events are registered upon confirmation from the device only; added switch capability; added Tone capability (beep command); combined Tuya commands; default settings are restored after the beep command; added capability 'Chime'; setVolume; volumeUp, volumeDown; playSound; beepVolume; playSoundVolume; playSoundDuration; unschedule() is called when preferences are updated.
1.0.0 2022-04-02 - First published version
